place.name: LOCHINVER
place.gazetteerText: Lochinver, vil. with pier, Assynt par., Sutherland, on Loch Inver; P.O., T.O.; has become a popular resort of tourists. (In 1887, John Bartholomew's Gazetteer of the British Isles)
